Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:42.85,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}静静地摇曳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.85,0:23:46.48,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}直到永远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.48,0:23:50.49,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}遥远的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:53.95,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}被悲伤浸染
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.16,0:23:58.41,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}肉体毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:03.21,ed,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be4}填入绝望
